{"word":"G1422 - δύσκολος - dýskolos - doo'-kol-os - Hard","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δύσκολος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dýskolos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">doo'-kol-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hard</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அரிதாயிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"difficult"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1418 - δυσ- - dys- - doos/1418\">G1418</a> and <b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;</b> <b>kolon</b> (<i>food</i>); properly <i>fastidious about eating</i> (<i>peevish</i>), that is, (generally) <i>impracticable:</i> - hard.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}